text: Kang Hyung-chul (born 21 February 1982) is a South Korean sport shooter who competed in the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport shooters Category:ISSF pistol shooters Category:Olympic shooters of South Korea Category:Shooters at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 2002 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in shooting Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 2002 Asian Games
